  <subsection xml:id="subsec-postal-charges">
    <title>Postal charges.</title>
    <p>
      These refers to the payments made for the services offered in a post office.
      In Kenya some of these services include:
    </p>
    <p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <p>
            Postage of letters and parcels 
            within the country and abroad.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>Postage of letters and parcels within the country and abroad.</li>
        <li>Sending money</li>
        <li>Banking</li>
        <li>Rental boxes</li>
      </ol>
    </p>
